Zandondo (wun jin wo wo'e, dagan IP address $1 bo) wo'a dama giyeko zheban ya{{sunna site}}
($4). Ezaloci nana {{DOKUN:$3|gbami yi|gbami zhi yi}} de alaka be email address nana'e:$2{{DOKUN:$3|ganmin giyeko eka tetengi nana|ganmin giyeko eka tetengi nana zhi}}wun ga zo tun eka {{PLURAL:$5|efo nini|$5 efozhi}}.
